Added XML Reader Interface, Enum, and Method. Javadoc'd and Comments

Delete of Files Update_data_Form_Account_From_File and Update_data_Observer as no longer needed due to XML package
Created and Coded Account Reader, Created MEdical_Reader and Unit Test classes
Medical Reader Code for getting and checking datetime of entry attribute, exiting xml reader when required (so dont need to iterate through it all when needing 1 entry.)
Refactor Medical Reader Refactoring due to different reader requirements for medical data when getting for latest, Daily, Export Is still ongoing but very close to finished
Refactor Medical Reader v2, Added checks for date and time when reading for daily,
Testing was attempted for XML reader with Robolectrec which failed, then started the Instrumentedtesting which will be more done today

Added and Deleted different files and directories, Will be removing more as testing occurs.
Finally solved the issue of not reading from files and alot of spare files and tests are currently present due to trying different fixes

Added Account Writer and started Code. Basic Unit Testing of XML Reader, but cannot do any more within JUnit due to complex logic and recursive calls. Mockito cant handle this with my current knowledge.

Added Account Writer and started Code. Basic Unit Testing of XML Reader, but cannot do any more within JUnit due to complex logic and recursive calls. Mockito cant handle this with my current knowledge.
Added New Test Suite for testing XML, This Commit Message also applies to previous commit, Forgot to update it.
Test Cases for Account Reader in XML_Test program

Testing Done for Account_Reader and Login_Reader
Modifications made to XML_Reader and all concrete classes, Added new String Parameter to Read_File() method required for the Login_reader.
Modified Login_Reader and Account_Reader loops and checks for the XML Pull Parser. Added new logic inside both classes that covert all the ENUMS to Strings to allow for simple x.equals(y) checks instead of conversions happening every loop.
Added new XML Test files, these will be presented at Group Meeting on 21st Sept 2018 on the layout and feedback will be gathered.
Due to Updates to files Javadocs will be modified at a later date to reflect changes

Modified Account Reader Error Messages for Clarity, Logic Statements for Readability, and Values checks for more NULLS to remove the change of errors
Modified Medical Reader Code due to errors from previous tests for Account and Login. This resulted in cleaner code and less methods as some where discovered to be nested for no reason. Modified the layout of the XML expected as well to make it easier to read and catch errors Modified Error Messages for Clarity, Logic Statements for Readability, and Values checks for more NULLS to remove the change of errors
Added Test Files for Medical reader, including new XML files

Updated Medical Reader Time Logic due to an error discovered. Currently nested If statements in a private method. If time permits this sprint will need to look at other methods for this check. Will be noted in JavaDoc for future
Finished Test Suite and all tests
Finished Java Doc for Account_Reader, Login_Reader, Medical_Reader, and XML_Reader, and added Excel documents with test results into the test/java/XML/xml_Test folder
